{"tid":2514940,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港全方位淪陷實例總合4(盡量每日更新)","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:49:11.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec97504120e4caacadcce7a465ad83294475a410","tid":2514940,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=2dabcd68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},{"pid":"bd0d3b7b38a71aa54179f8aa42567789fc94b3d7","tid":2514940,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e51a96b67a11a4b0bd2f03b6cf45a4a020b89fe","tid":2514940,"uid":140125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"黑警撚樣全部不得善終"},{"pid":"e9536b663d5034f91e78071180cab962e7be4592","tid":2514940,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:48:58.000Z","msg":"任職銀行律師的美籍漢，前年在銅鑼灣港鐵站捲入休班警追截懷疑跳閘⻘年的糾紛，被控襲擊休班警，案件今在東區裁判法院續審。被告接受控方盤問時強調，事發時一直不知道事主是警察，皆因事主多次否認，而且其行為亦不似警察。至於他踩著事主是為了拉走警棍，防止事主繼續用以襲擊途人。案件審結，押後至6月21日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n控方又指，被告用腳踩著俞是要當眾羞辱他，並作為進一步的襲擊。被告不同意，解釋指當時意識不到有群眾圍觀，而他此舉是要拉走俞手中警棍，因他目睹俞曾在港鐵站內用警棍襲擊幾位途人，擔心若他保管著警棍會繼續施襲。控方質疑當時被告已站了起來，俞則繼續倒地，顯示被告已控制了俞；被告不同意。<br />\n<br />\n控方追問，既然他以為被告有精神問題，又如何肯定俞自稱不是警察之說屬實。被告解釋，俞當時以不同言語一再否認自己是警察，加上以他作為律師的觀察，俞的行為不合符警隊守則。"},{"pid":"75bc60f962e59fd864f4a94b0b14b3415d72d8a3","tid":2514940,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:49:11.000Z","msg":"1930 香港這一天<br />\n利君雅被港台剷走<br />\n鏗鏘集頭條新聞無得留底<br />\n李百全新官上任「文革發動」日日有新聞<br />\n政治不正確節目下架<br />\n五夜講場議事論事youtube下架<br />\n（眾新聞 香港這一天）<br />\nMay 4, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j0b_Z-c0yUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj0b_Z-c0yUw&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a08f5630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j0b_Z-c0yUw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n91.1K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n港台新官上任，日日有「獨家」新聞，昨日有利君雅合約、節目下架。港台今早一項活動上，有寫上「文革發動」的直幡，耐人尋味。利君雅的質問方式、部份節目被裁定超越「紅線」，一律被鏟走。楊健興分析港台，各位點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=6bc3dc03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com</a>"}]}